<html>
<body>
If your students learn only one thing in this unit, make sure they understand that <strong>valid engineering claims require evidence and reasoning.</strong>  The evidence must be appropriate/sufficient and the reasoning must be based on scientific/mathematical principles.

All lessons are 1 day (50 min) unless otherwise stated.

<strong>BEFORE YOU BEGIN:</strong>
<a href="https://www.piazza.com/class/j7w3w7cgmaw4cg?cid=24">Forming Groups</a>*
Careers Research Project
Pretest

